short_desc: If INMEMWORS=1,2 then DECCOGIN should equal 1
full_desc: If A2 Q6. INMEMWORS (participant's memory is worse?)=1,2 (Yes) then B9 Q4. DECCOGIN (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If INMEMTROUB=4,5 then DECCOGIN should equal 1
full_desc: If A2 Q7. INMEMTROUB (participant trouble remembering?)=4,5 (Often or very often) then B9 Q4. DECCOGIN (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If INMEMTEN=4,5 then DECCOGIN should equal 1
full_desc: If A2 Q8. INMEMTEN (participant's memory compared to 10 years ago?)=4,5 (Much worse or a little worse) then B9 Q4. DECCOGIN (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If PARKSIGN = 1 then MOMOPARK should equal 1
full_desc: If B8 Q3. PARKSIGN (parkinsonian signs) = 1 (Yes), then Q17. MOMOPARK (motor symptoms suggestive of parkinsonism) should = 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If PARKSIGN = 0 then MOMOPARK should equal 0
full_desc: If B8 Q3. PARKSIGN (parkinsonian signs) = 0 (No abnormal signs in this section are present), then Q17. MOMOPARK (motor symptoms suggestive of parkinsonism) should = 0 (No)

short_desc: If MASKING= 1, MOFACE should not be 0
full_desc: If B8 Q3m. MASKING (Facial expression) = 1 (present), then Q15f. MOFACE (Change in facial expression) should not be 0 (no)
If B8 Q3m. MASKING (Facial expression) = 0 (absent), then Q15f. MOFACE (Change in facial expression) should = 0 (no)

short_desc: If GAITABN= 1, MOGAIT should not be 0
full_desc: If B8 Q5. GAITABN (Gait) = 1 (present), then Q15a. MOGAIT (Gait disorder) should not be 0 (no)
If B8 Q5. GAITABN (Gait) = 0 (absent), then Q15a. MOGAIT (Gait disorder) should = 0 (no)

test_name: MCI or dementia diagnoses on D1a align with COGAGE on B9
short_desc: If DEMENTED=1 or MCI=1 then COGAGE should not be blank
full_desc: If Form D1a Q3. DEMENTED (Dementia?)=1 (yes) or Form D1a Q4b. MCI  (MCI (amnestic or non-amnestic)?) =1 (yes) then Q9i. COGAGE (Age that prominent cognitive problem began) should not be blank

test_name: Normal diagnosis on D1a aligns with DECCLIN on B9
short_desc: If NORMCOG=0 then DECCLIN should equal 1
full_desc: If Form D1a Q2. NORMCOG (Unimpaired cognition & behavior?)=0 (No) then Q7. DECCLIN (Participant experiencing symptoms or declines per clinician) should equal 1 (Yes)

test_name: Normal diagnosis on D1a aligns with DECCLIN on B9
short_desc: If NORMCOG=1 then DECCLIN should not equal 1
full_desc: If Form D1a Q2. NORMCOG (Unimpaired cognition & behavior?)=1 (Yes) then Q7. DECCLIN (Participant experiencing symptoms or declines per clinician) should not equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If MEMWORS=1,2 then DECCOG should equal 1
full_desc: If A1 Q18. MEMWORS (participant's memory is worse?)=1,2 (Yes) then B9 Q1. DECCOG (Participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If MEMTROUB=4,5 then DECCOG should equal 1
full_desc: If A1 Q19. MEMTROUB (participant trouble remembering?)=4,5 (Often or very often) then B9 Q1. DECCOG (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If MEMTEN=4,5 then DECCOG should equal 1
full_desc: If A1 Q20. MEMTEN (participant's memory compared to 10 years ago?)=4,5 (Much worse or a little worse) then B9 Q1. DECCOG (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)
